These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: disaster, romance, time-travel, drama, crime, western, epic
There are 7 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, colombian, indonesian, nigerian, spanish
 1. the chinese is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
 2. the chinese is on the right of the indonesian##1
 3. the chinese is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
 4. the spanish is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the british is the person watching drama movies##1
 6. the brazilian is in the middle##1
 7. the colombian is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is in an even position##4
 9. the nigerian is in an odd position##4
10. the nigerian is on the left or right of the spanish##3
11. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the nigerian##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is the indonesian##1
13. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
14. the person watching crime movies is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |    6    |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime      | time-travel      | western    | epic    | romance | disaster     | drama     |
| Nationality   | colombian | indonesian | chinese | brazilian | nigerian   | spanish | british |

