.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-2::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, montecristo, havana, old-henry, dunhill, siglo, vegafina
7 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, goat, hamster, hedgehog, pony, rat
 1. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the montecristo-smoker##3
 2. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
 3. the owner of the hedgehog is in an odd position##4
 4. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the owner of the hamster##3
 5. the dunhill-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the owner of the pony is the old-henry-smoker##1
 7. the montecristo-smoker is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 9. the old-henry-smoker is the owner of the pony##1
10. the havana-smoker is between the owner of the pony and the montecristo-smoker##2
11. the siglo-smoker is in the middle##1
12. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
13. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
14. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |    3    |     4      |      5      |     6     |   7    |
| Cigar   | montecristo   | havana | old-henry | siglo   | vegafina | baccarat | dunhill |
| Pet           | hedgehog | cat          | pony    | chinchilla | hamster     | goat      | rat    |

