.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-3::.
There 7 different types of food: artichoke, cucumber, eggplant, kale, kiwi, nectarine, onion
House: palace, victorian, art-deco, colonial, farmhouse, futuristic, cape-cod
 1. the art-deco house is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 2. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
 3. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 4. the person eating cucumber is between the person eating nectarine and the person eating kale##2
 5. the futuristic house is on the left or right of the victorian house##3
 6. the art-deco house is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
 7. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
 8. the palace house is on the far left##1
 9. the victorian house is the person eating artichoke##1
10. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
11. the futuristic house is the person eating onion##1
12. the farmhouse house is between the person eating eggplant and the person eating onion##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |       5        |        6        |     7      |
| Food   | kale        | cucumber  | nectarine | eggplant | kiwi           | onion           | artichoke  |
| House    | palace | colonial | cape-cod   | art-deco    | farmhouse | futuristic | victorian |

