 3. the paramedic is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 4. the writer is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
 7. the paramedic is in an odd position##4
 8. the designer is on the far right##1
 9. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing poker##1
10. the videographer is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
11. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing chess##1
12. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
13. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the teacher##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4      |      5       |      6      |      7      |
| Game   | chess | snooker    | poker | domino | backgammon      | billiard | monopoly |
| Job     | writer  | accountant | paramedic   | fisherman  | videographer | teacher     | designer    |

