 4. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3
 5. the ranch-style house is between the farmhouse house and the cottage house##2
 6. the fan of punk is in an even position##4
 7. the gothic-revival house is the fan of jazz##1
 8. the victorian house is on the left or right of the wooden house##3
 9. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
11. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
12. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of r&b is the victorian house##1
14. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
15. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
16. the wooden house is on the right of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
