The people prefer 7 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, golf, surfing, swimming, tennis, volleyball
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
 4. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
 6. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the person who's sport is volleyball##3
 7. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 9. the person who's sport is swimming is in an even position##4
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the person who's sport is surfing is in the middle##1
12. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the tram##1
13. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |    3    |    4    |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | motorbike    | helicopter | quad-bike    | tram    | scooter       | ship      |
| Sport         | climbing | swimming | golf    | surfing | tennis | volleyball | biathlon |

