 3. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person who's birthday is in june and the owner of the cat##2
 6. the owner of the hamster is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
11. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
12. the owner of the fish is the person who's birthday is in june##1
13. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |   3   |   4   |   5    |  6   |    7    |
