 9. the prince-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking tea is between the bongani-smoker and the person drinking mirinda##2
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
12. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |   4   |    5    |       6       |      7      |
| Beverage   | milk     | mirinda   | tea      | fanta | cola    | hot-chocolate | almond-milk |
| Cigar       | prince | swisher | cain | bongani  | siglo | vegafina     | ritmeester    |

