.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-4-19::.
There 7 different types of food: apple, apricot, artichoke, cabbage, grapes, kale, radish
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, ship, airplane, jet-ski, helicopter, trike
 1. the person eating apricot is the person driving the helicopter##1
 2. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
 3. the person driving the jet-ski is the person eating radish##1
 4. the person driving the trike is the person eating kale##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is in the middle##1
 6. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
 8. the person eating grapes is the person driving the ship##1
 9. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the car##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
12. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
13. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person eating apple##1
14. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |     5     |    6    |    7    |
| Food          | cabbage  | apricot | apple     | radish  | artichoke | kale    | grapes  |
| Transport   | airplane | helicopter  | bus | jet-ski | car | trike | ship |

